# Ignore build artifacts
**/bin/
**/obj/

# Ignore .env files (keep .env.example)
**/.env
**/.env.local

# Ignore IDE files
**/.vs/
**/.vscode/
**/.idea/

# Ignore OS files
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db

# Ignore git
**/.git/
**/.gitignore

# Ignore documentation (already in image)
**/README.md
**/CONTRIBUTING.md
**/docs/

# Ignore test files
**/tests/
**/*.Tests/
